Skin Name: ClearSky

Original Author: Will Reinhart

Authors Note: Based on the clearlooks-deepsky GTK2 and metacity theme, using 
Green with Envy as a template.  

Thanks to: Richard Stellingwerff (remenic @ gmail . com) for Clearlooks, 
and Lokheed @ gmail . com for Green with Envy

